# Environment Variables Reference

All secrets live in `.env.local`. **Never commit `.env.local` to Git.**

Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in your values.

```bash
# ─── Google AI ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GEMINI_API_KEY=
GOOGLE_CLOUD_PROJECT=

# ─── Anthropic Claude (Affidavit Decoder & Misinfo Shield) ───────────────────
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# ─── Upstash Redis (Translation cache & Queue reporting) ─────────────────────
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=

# ─── Google Maps (Booth Locator) ─────────────────────────────────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=

# ─── App ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://localhost:3000
```
